text: 237px ' (March 13, 1656 – September 15, 1678) was a Japanese daimyō of the Edo period, who ruled the Tokushima Domain. His court title was Awa no kami. ==Family== * Father: Hachisuka Mitsutaka * Mother: Kinhime (d.1703) * Wife: Reishoin ==Reference== Category:1656 births Category:1678 deaths Category:Daimyo Category:Hachisuka clan
